# Allow this widget to be embedded as a cross-origin iframe inside a
# cross-origin-isolated (COEP: require-corp) host such as the Tarsk app.
#
# `require-corp` is used (not `credentialless`) because it is supported across
# both Chromium and WebKit (Electrobun's macOS webview is WebKit, which does not
# support the `credentialless` COEP value or anonymous iframes). The widget's own
# cross-origin fetches must return CORS headers to remain allowed under require-corp.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: cross-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
